          </para>
          <para>
            <text><citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM174084">Section 260(1)</extref></citation>: add:</text>
            <amend increment="1" quote="1">
              <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">c</label>
                <para>
                  <text>the name of a district or region of a local authority described in Part 1 or Part 2 of Schedule 2 is altered under <citation jurisdiction="nz">section 11(2)</citation> of the New Zealand Geographic Board (Ngā Pou Taunaha o Aotearoa) Act 2008.</text>
                </para>
