                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">7A</label>
                <para>
                  <text>Before the decision of the Minister becomes final under subsection (7), the proposal must, to the extent that it relates to the proposed name of the proposed marine reserve, be referred to the New Zealand Geographic Board under <citation jurisdiction="nz">section 27(2) or 30</citation> of the New Zealand Geographic Board (Ngā Pou Taunaha o Aotearoa) Act 2008, as the case may be.</text>
                </para>
